    { "@type": "Question", "name": "What is the median house price in Clayfield Brisbane?", "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Clayfield sits at the prestige end of the inner north-east market. Heritage-listed Queenslanders and large character homes on generous blocks trade in a range that reflects the suburb's position alongside Ascot and Hamilton as one of Brisbane's most established northside markets. Stock is limited and demand from quality buyers is consistent. Contact Daniel for a current appraisal on your specific property." } },
